2
00:00:02,220 --> 00:00:04,930
I promised Misuzu and Carol
I'd walk home with them today.

3
00:00:04,930 --> 00:00:07,140
It's cool. Don't worry about it.

4
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:09,060
You're taking this awfully well, Jun-kun.

5
00:00:09,060 --> 00:00:10,780
Not going to get all dejected this time?

6
00:00:10,780 --> 00:00:14,410
I'll never get dejected over not
going home together anymore.

7
00:00:14,410 --> 00:00:17,820
I don't want to be the kind
of guy who ties Tomo down.

8
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:18,810
Jun...

9
00:00:21,110 --> 00:00:24,100
What the... S-Stop!

10
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:28,880
Lately... Actually, for a while now...

11
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:32,630
I think it started when he started
to see me as a girl, to be honest...

12
00:00:33,090 --> 00:00:36,890
