it's actually kinda pissing me off.

13
00:00:36,890 --> 00:00:37,680
I get it.

14
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:38,640
I get it, too.

15
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:40,600
It's like I'm the only one freaking out,

16
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:43,560
