25
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:07,920
It'll be Christmas soon.

26
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,960
Why don't you go see this together?

27
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:28,980
When I throw a jab or a straight,
it always lands

28
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:34,110
But when I'm aiming for your heart,
I miss every time

29
00:01:34,110 --> 00:01:39,450
Parallel, zigzagging, awkward, incoherent

30
00:01:39,450 --> 00:01:43,950
When you look my way and move closer to me

31
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:49,710
I know it doesn't mean the same thing for you

32
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:54,760
But I wish we could stay like this forever

33
00:01:54,760 --> 00:02:00,890
My changing feelings are driving me crazy

34
00:02:00,890 --> 00:02:06,180
The moment you turn to face me,
take that! Telepathy

35
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:11,650
If only we could feel the same thing

36
00:02:11,650 --> 00:02:16,530
I want to kick this pesky subtlety away

37
00:02:16,530 --> 00:02:22,530
I want to know everything,
I want to know everything

38
00:02:22,530 --> 00:02:25,080
I can't fool you forever

39
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,710
I can't keep this hidden

40
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:32,460
I want to shout out my secret, AHHH

41
00:02:34,380 --> 00:02:36,920
Take that! Telepathy

42
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:39,380
