46
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,360
Jun!

47
00:03:00,070 --> 00:03:01,320
Did you wait long?

48
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:07,040
You look kinda grown-up today.

49
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,500
You think so?

50
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:10,830
