53
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:19,670
You look... cute today. Pretty, in fact.

54
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:23,760
There's just something special
about this look. I really like it.

55
00:03:25,970 --> 00:03:31,020
Sorry... I'm not used to this kind
of thing, so I can't say it well...

56
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:33,190
Y-Yeah...

57
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:35,520
Damn him!

58
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,610
We're gonna see this today!

59
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:42,530
