62
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:48,410
This Love Is the Real Deal!! A Story of Pure Love

63
00:03:44,660 --> 00:03:48,410
C'mon, Jun. We're not little kids anymore.

64
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:51,870
