135
00:08:07,090 --> 00:08:11,010
I came here today... to kiss you!

136
00:08:11,010 --> 00:08:12,120
Kiss me?!

137
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:15,800
T-To kiss me?! Where did that even...

138
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,850
