143
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,280
Huh?! Jun?!

144
00:08:33,570 --> 00:08:34,910
Is it gonna happen?!

145
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:35,990
Are we...

146
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:38,070
