147
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,120
He's making a fist?!

148
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,400
Is that a thing, too?!

149
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,210
What?!

150
00:08:46,210 --> 00:08:48,790
What the hell are you doing?! Are you okay?!

151
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:50,840
Tomo...

152
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:54,010
You have so much appeal!

153
00:08:55,010 --> 00:09:00,810
The desire to kiss you... a-and touch you...
is constantly on my mind!

154
00:09:00,810 --> 00:09:01,970
Huh?!

155
00:09:01,970 --> 00:09:05,640
