213
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:07,580
Just wait a minute!

214
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:08,540
Shut up!

215
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:11,040
I said wait, Tomo!

216
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:19,200
Do you know why I'm pissed off?

217
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:21,920
Because I didn't tell
you what your dad said?

218
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:24,720
Bingo. Why didn't you tell me?

219
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,890
Because...

220
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:28,850
You could have just told me

221
00:12:28,850 --> 00:12:32,560
that you'd go kick my dad's ass,
so I could just take it easy and wait!

222
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,020
Then I would've...

223
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:36,980
I can't just ask you to wait for me!

224
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:43,240
I don't... have to wait?

225
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:47,950
Yeah. Since it's come to this,
I intend to face it with all I've got.

226
00:12:48,410 --> 00:12:51,950
But I know it's not gonna be
that easy to beat your dad.

227
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:56,880
Defeating him was already my life's goal.

228
00:12:57,200 --> 00:13:01,800
So if I go through my whole
life never able to beat him,

229
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,130
I'll just...

230
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,930
Get...

231
