Get real!

232
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:15,230
As long as Jun's like that, he'll never win,
no matter how capable he is!

233
00:13:16,810 --> 00:13:18,520
Long time no see.

234
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:21,320
How have you been, Tomo-chan?

235
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:24,570
You completely ignored us
all through winter break,

236
00:13:24,570 --> 00:13:26,200
so I guess it's been two weeks?

237
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:29,910
Do you remember when we said
we'd all go skiing together?

238
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:33,450
Um... I'm... really sorry...

239
00:13:34,410 --> 00:13:36,790
So that's what happened.

240
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:39,460
Well? Do you think he can win?

241
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:41,130
H-He can!

242
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:43,510
Maybe not right away, but...

243
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:47,260
If he takes his training seriously,
maybe in a few months...

244
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:49,300
No, maybe a few years...

245
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:50,510
That's too long.

246
00:13:50,850 --> 00:13:53,390
So what are you going to do?

247
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:58,180
What do you want me to say?
There's nothing I can do.

248
00:13:58,560 --> 00:13:59,940
And that's okay with you?

249
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:05,110
